definitions.definition: A newly hatched bird, reptile or other animal that has emerged from an egg .
examples: The hatchling alligator had just broken out of its shell but was already trying to follow its mother, who hunted hatchling birds.

definitions.definition: A person who has (especially recently ) realized that they are transgender .

main_definition: A newly hatched bird, reptile or other animal that has emerged from an egg .
secondary_definitions: ( transgender slang ) A person who has (especially recently ) realized that they are transgender .
